172 A.3d 1087 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. WILLIAM A. MARSHALL, A/K/A BILL A. BERRY, DOLLAR BI MARSHALL, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-288 September Term 2017

079506 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002974-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
